{
  "texts": [
    "For sequential circuits, AutoBench has 3.36 times Eval2 pass@1 ratio compared with the baseline.• Then please insert your LLM API key into config/key_API.json before running the project.• Do not forget to change the bin path of iverilog you installed in iverilog_call.py.",
    "• At last, you can run a CMB task demo via \"python main.py -d cmb\" to make sure you have correctly setup the project.",
    "Then you can run \"python main.py -d 156\" for the whole experiment, or run AutoBench on specific tasks according to the guidance in README.",
    "6.3.2 Hardware dependencies Check README at https://github.c om/AutoBench/AutoBenchor section 6.1 Hardware.",
    "6.3.3 Software dependencies Check README at https://github.c om/AutoBench/AutoBenchor subsection 6.3.1."
  ]
}